data.description: Welcome to this charming property that has a perfect blend of convenience, spacious living, and unique features. Nestled near Stillhouse Lake and the town of Salado, this home sits on a generous 0.579 acre lot, providing ample space for various activities. As you approach, you'll be greeted by a large 20 by 40 foot shop on the property, equipped with RV hook-ups and power, providing versatility for hobbyists or those in need of extra storage space. The interior of the home boasts a welcoming ambiance with stained concrete floors, recessed lighting, and tall ceilings. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen, creating an inviting space for entertaining. The kitchen features an island with a breakfast bar area and stands out with the unique presence of two pantries, ensuring abundant storage for all your culinary needs. The living room is adorned with a stone wood-burning fireplace, adding a cozy touch to the space. The main bedroom is a retreat on its own with an ensuite bathroom that includes a separate shower, separate bathtub, and dual vanities. An intriguing feature of this property is the presence of another bedroom with an ensuite bathroom, conveniently connected to a separate garage area – perfect for accommodating guests with privacy. Step outside to discover a delightful oasis with an above-ground pool surrounded by manicured and well-kept landscaping and lawn. The fencing, only two years old, adds a touch of security and privacy to the outdoor space. Noteworthy updates include a brand-new water heater and water softener, both less than a month old, ensuring modern comfort and efficiency. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this property your own – schedule a private showing today!
